Problem Statement
1.Statement
Write a program that takes three numbers and prints their sum. Every number is given on a separate line.

a = int(input())
b = int(input())
c = int(input())
print(a + b +c)

2.Write a program that greets the person by printing the word "Hi" and the name of the person. 

code:
name = input("Please enter your name: ")
print("Hi", name)

3.Write a program that takes a number and print its square.

 n = float(input())
print(n ** 2)

4.Write a program that reads the length of the base and the height of a right-angled triangle and prints the area. Every number is given on a separate line.

base = float(input())
height = float(input())
area = 0.5 * base * height
print(area)

